SQL_STMT_U.val: select cast ((sum (CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESMAN) + sum (CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESAUTO) - sum (CMON_TOTSALCREDNOTESMAN) - sum (CMON_TOTSALCREDNOTESAUTO)) as decimal (13,2)), cast ((sum (CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESMAN) + sum (CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESAUTO)) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/CMON where CMON_ADMNO = :2 and CMON_CLNTNO = :3 and CMON_YEAR = :4 and CMON_MONTH <> :5 and CMON_CURRENCY = ':6' for fetch only

select cast ((sum (CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESMAN) + sum (CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESAUTO) - sum (CMON_TOTSALCREDNOTESMAN) - sum (CMON_TOTSALCREDNOTESAUTO)) as decimal (13,2)), cast ((sum (CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESMAN) + sum (CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESAUTO)) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/CMON where CMON_ADMNO = :2 and CMON_CLNTNO = :3 and CMON_YEAR = :4 and CMON_CURRENCY = ':5' for fetch only
select count(*) from :1/CMON where CMON_ADMNO = :2 and CMON_CLNTNO = :3 and CMON_YEAR = :4 and CMON_MONTH <> :5 and CMON_CURRENCY = ':6' for fetch only
select count(*) from :1/CMON where CMON_ADMNO = :2 and CMON_CLNTNO = :3 and CMON_YEAR = :4 and CMON_CURRENCY = ':5' for fetch only

select cast (sum (CMON_TOTAPAIDINVXDAYSFROINVDAT) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum (CMON_TOTAPAIDINVXDAYSFRODUEDAT) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum (CMON_TOTAPAIDINV) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/CMON where CMON_ADMNO = :2 and CMON_CLNTNO = :3 and CMON_YEAR = :4 and CMON_CURRENCY = ':5' for fetch only

select cast (sum (CMON_LIQRATIO1) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum (CMON_LIQRATIO2) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/CMON where CMON_ADMNO = :2 and CMON_CLNTNO = :3 and CMON_YEAR = :4 and CMON_MONTH <> :5 and CMON_CURRENCY = ':6' for fetch only

select cast (sum (CMON_LIQRATIO1) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum (CMON_LIQRATIO2) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum (CMON_TOTAPAIDINVXDAYSFROINVDAT) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum (CMON_TOTAPAIDINVXDAYSFRODUEDAT) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum (CMON_TOTAPAIDINV) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/CMON where CMON_ADMNO = :2 and CMON_CLNTNO = :3 and CMON_YEAR = :4 and CMON_CURRENCY = ':5' for fetch only

select cast ((sum (CMOC_CURRBALFACTACC) + sum (CMOC_CURRBALSPECIALACC)) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/CMOC where CMOC_ADMNO = :2 and CMOC_CLNTNO = :3 and CMOC_YEAR = :4 and CMOC_MONTH = :5 and CMOC_CURRENCY = ':6' and CMOC_COUNTRY = ':7' for fetch only

select cast ((sum (CMOC_CURRBALFACTACC) + sum (CMOC_CURRBALSPECIALACC)) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/CMOC where CMOC_ADMNO = :2 and CMOC_CLNTNO = :3 and CMOC_YEAR = :4 and CMOC_MONTH = :5 and CMOC_CURRENCY = ':6' and CMOC_COUNTRY <> ':7' for fetch only
select cast ((sum (CMCD_SPECIALACCOUNTH) + sum (CMCD_DISPUTESGROSSH)) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/CMCD where CMCD_ADMNO = :2 and CMCD_CLNTNO = :3 for fetch only
select cast (sum (CPKC_BALANCE) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/CPKC where CPKC_ADMNO = :2 and CPKC_CLNTNO = :3 and CPKC_INDIVIDUAL = ':4' and CPKC_DATE = ':5' for fetch only
select cast ((sum (ACCC_MUTAFACTORING) + sum (ACCC_MUTASPECIAL)) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/ACCC where ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = :2 and ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO = :3 for fetch only

select cast ((sum (CMON_CURRBALFACTACC) + sum (CMON_CURRBALSPECIALACC)) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum (CMON_TOTNDEBTORS) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum (CMON_TOTNDEBTORSACTIVE) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum (CMON_TOTNCREDNOTESOUT) as decimal (13,2)), cast ((sum (CMON_TOTSALCREDNOTESAUTO) + sum (CMON_TOTSALCREDNOTESMAN)) as decimal (13,2)), cast ((sum (CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESAUTO) + sum (CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESMAN)) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum (CMON_CURRBALCREDNOTES) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum (CMON_CURRBALDEBTNOTES) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/CMON where CMON_ADMNO = :2 and CMON_CLNTNO = :3 and CMON_YEAR = :4 and CMON_MONTH = :5 and CMON_CURRENCY = ':6' for fetch only
